really alpha right now.

commands :

^Q quit
^S save

^U undo
^R redo/repeat
^T repeat till current line

^A (begin) begin of line
^E (end) end of line
^B back one word
^F forward one word

^D (del) del character under cursor
^H (backspace) del character before cursor

^L del to end of line
^K kill word before

^@ (^space) start selection
^C copy line/selection
^X delete line/selection
^V paste at cursor position

^W enter search pattern
^Y first occurence of search
^N search next
^P search previous

^G goto line (or begin/end)
^J justify
^I (tab) indent/complete
^M (enter)
^[ (esc) jump to previous position
^O open line before
^Z change Case

(insert) insert next char litteraly

flag :

F1  line number (+redraw)
F2  auto indent
F3  highligth search
